{"tid":2065803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧據報周三夏威夷美軍基地晤中方官員","createTime":"2020-06-15T23:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T03:04:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cea8955c64e469c83d7a0d72277903d936ff0e0","tid":2065803,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧據報周三夏威夷美軍基地晤中方官員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532273-20200616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532273-20200616.htm&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7nfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=2d4a425c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532273-20200616.htm&h=b717684c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532273-20200616.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息人士報道，美國國務卿蓬佩奧計劃今個星期在夏威夷的美軍基地，與中國代表團會面，討論自今年初惡化的雙邊關係。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，蓬佩奧預計當地星期二由華盛頓啟程到夏威夷，星期三在希卡姆空軍基地與中方代表團會面，議題可能包括應對新型肺炎疫情、軍備控制、貿易、香港、北韓，以及中美互相採取針對記者的行動。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅昨日表示，中美外交管道保持著溝通，如果有進一步消息，中方將及時發布。"},{"pid":"2477c77b03a9cb0aa367ef8247bd9d2b1dcd72f2","tid":2065803,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:58:10.000Z","msg":"中國咪撚縮呀 20號要立國安法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b075cafecfdff449e19943fd1a12af9da7bae544","tid":2065803,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"唔好放過解體中共既機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3981c0e38f6f5db3d3c622411842c7918c86545b","tid":2065803,"uid":360864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited